vec.truncate(8);
assert_eq!(vec, [1, 2, 3]);
```

[Run](https://play.rust-lang.org/?code=%23!%5Ballow(unused)%5D%0Afn+main()+%7B%0A++++let+mut+vec+=+vec!%5B1,+2,+3%5D;%0A++++vec.truncate(8);%0A++++assert_eq!(vec,+%5B1,+2,+3%5D);%0A%7D&edition=2021)

